    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, i run a small local hardware store in a pretty rural area where cost of living isn't too high. we've been hearing some talk about raising the minimum wage again. from a business standpoint, how do those kinds of changes usually play out for places like mine?",
      "source": "evaluator"
